Structs/ZlibHeader/CompressionLevel.html.name: CompressionLevel

Structs/GzipHeader/FileSystemType.html#/.name: unix
Structs/GzipHeader/FileSystemType.html#/.abstract: One of many Linux systems. (It seems like modern macOS systems also fall into this category).

Structs/GzipHeader/FileSystemType.html#/.name: unknown
Structs/GzipHeader/FileSystemType.html#/.abstract: File system was unknown to the archiver.

Structs/GzipHeader/FileSystemType.html#/.name: other
Structs/GzipHeader/FileSystemType.html#/.abstract: File system was one of the rare systems..

Structs/GzipHeader/FileSystemType.html.name: FileSystemType
Structs/GzipHeader/FileSystemType.html.abstract: Type of file system on which gzip archive was created.

Structs/GzipHeader.html#/s:vV13SWCompres.name: compressionMethod
Structs/GzipHeader.html#/s:vV13SWCompres.abstract: Compression method of archive. Always equals to .deflate.

Structs/GzipHeader.html#/s:vV13SWCompres.abstract: The most recent modification time of the original file. If set to 0 (default value == unset), then nil.

Structs/GzipHeader.html#/s:vV13SWCompres.name: osType
Structs/GzipHeader.html#/s:vV13SWCompres.abstract: Type of file system on which compression took place.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: wrongMagic
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: Either magic number in header or footer was not equal to predefined value.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: wrongArchiveInfo
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: One of special fields of archive had an incorrect value.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: fieldReservedValue
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: One of special fields of archive had a reserved value.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: wrongInfoCRC
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: Checksum of one of special fields of archive was incorrect.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: wrongFilterID
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: ID of filter(s) used in archvie was unsupported.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: checkTypeSHA256
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: Type of checksum of archive was SHA-256.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: wrongDataSize
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: Either size of decompressed data was not equal to specified one in block header or

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: wrongCheck
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: Computed checksum of uncompressed data didn’t match the value stored in the archive.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: wrongPadding
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: Unsupported padding of a structure in the archive.

Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.name: multiByteIntegerError
Enums/XZError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression7.abstract: Either null byte encountered or exceeded maximum amount bytes during reading multi byte number.

Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: wrongHuffmanGroups
Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Wrong number of Huffman tables/groups (should be between 2 and 6).

Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: wrongSelector
Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Selector was greater than total number of Huffman tables/groups.

Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: wrongHuffmanLengthCode
Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Wrong code of Huffman length (should be between 0 and 20).

Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: symbolNotFound
Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Symbol was not found in Huffman tree.

Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: wrongCRC
Enums/BZip2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Computed CRC of uncompressed data didn’t match the value stored in the archive.

Enums/DeflateError.html#/s:FO13SWCompres.name: wrongUncompressedBlockLengths
Enums/DeflateError.html#/s:FO13SWCompres.abstract: Uncompressed block’ length and nlength bytes were not compatible.

Enums/DeflateError.html#/s:FO13SWCompres.name: wrongSymbol
Enums/DeflateError.html#/s:FO13SWCompres.abstract: Decoded symbol was found in Huffman tree but is unknown.

Enums/DeflateError.html#/s:FO13SWCompres.name: symbolNotFound
Enums/DeflateError.html#/s:FO13SWCompres.abstract: Symbol was not found in Huffman tree.

Enums/ZlibError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongCompressionMethod
Enums/ZlibError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Compression method was other than 8 which is the only supported one.

Enums/ZlibError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongCompressionInfo
Enums/ZlibError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Compression info was greater than 7 which is uncompatible number 8 compression method.

Enums/ZlibError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongFcheck
Enums/ZlibError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: First two bytes were inconsistent with each other.

Enums/ZlibError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongAdler32
Enums/ZlibError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Computed Adler-32 sum of uncompressed data didn’t match the value stored in the archive.

Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: exceededUncompressedSize
Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: The number of uncompressed bytes hit limit in the middle of decoding.

Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: windowIsEmpty
Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Unable to perfrom repeat-distance decoding because there is nothing to repeat.

Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: rangeDecoderFinishError
Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: End of stream marker is reached, but range decoder is in incorrect state.

Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: repeatWillExceed
Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: The number of bytes to repeat is greater than the amount bytes that is left to decode.

Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: notEnoughToRepeat
Enums/LZMAError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: The amount of already decoded bytes is smaller than repeat length.

Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.name: notFoundCentralDirectoryEnd
Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.abstract: End of Central Directoty record was not found.

Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.name: wrongSignature
Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.abstract: Wrong signature of one of ZIP container’s structures.

Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.name: wrongSize
Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.abstract: Wrong either compressed or uncompressed size of a ZIP container’s entry.

Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.name: wrongVersion
Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.abstract: Wrong number of version needed to extract ZIP container.

Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.name: multiVolumesNotSupported
Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.abstract: Archive either spanned or consists of several volumes. This feature is not supported.

Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.name: encryptionNotSupported
Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.abstract: Entry or record is encrypted. This feature is not supported.

Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.name: patchingNotSupported
Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.abstract: Entry contains patched data. This feature is not supported.

Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.name: wrongCRC32
Enums/ZipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompression.abstract: Computed CRC32 of entry’s data didn’t match the value stored in the container.

Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongMagic
Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: First two bytes of archive were not 31 and 139.

Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongCompressionMethod
Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Compression method was other than 8 which is the only supported one.

Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongFlags
Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Reserved flags bits were not equal to 0.

Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongHeaderCRC
Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Computed CRC of header didn’t match the value stored in the archive.

Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongCRC
Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Computed CRC of uncompressed data didn’t match the value stored in the archive.

Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.name: wrongISize
Enums/GzipError.html#/s:FO13SWCompressio.abstract: Computed isize didn’t match the value stored in the archive.

Enums/LZMA2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: wrongProperties
Enums/LZMA2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Reserved bits of LZMA2 properties byte were not equal to zero.

Enums/LZMA2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: wrongControlByte
Enums/LZMA2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Unknown conrol byte value of LZMA2 packet.

Enums/LZMA2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: wrongReset
Enums/LZMA2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Unknown reset instruction encounetered in LZMA2 packet.

Enums/LZMA2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.name: wrongSizes
Enums/LZMA2Error.html#/s:FO13SWCompressi.abstract: Either size of decompressed data was not equal to specified one in LZMA2 packet or
